Elen Willard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elen_Willard 0 Elen Willard (born September 1, 1941) is a former American character actress who worked in American network dramatic television series from 1960 to 1966. Her first aired performance was a supporting role in a 1960 episode of the short-lived CBS detective series Markham.
